data.description: Great Boasting 5.9 acres ,Minisink school district! Close to highways, this brick house has an ideal commuter location. The house has been completely renovated. It features a brand new kitchen with granite counter/stainless steel appliances, a brand new bath, new water heater and hardwood floors as seen. A wood-burning fireplace and a wood-burning stove will not only give you enough warmth in winter, but will also bring down the utility cost! The spacious basement was beautifully done, adding an additional 700+ sf living space. The total square footage includes the basement. CO for basement obtained. New gutter system. Boasting 5.9 acres and 444 feet of road frontage, the nice property has great subdivision potential! Live in the house and subdivide the property. You can increase the value of the property instantly!
